{
  "stem": "16313.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because there was a lot of minorities in Poland-- Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I got experience.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we go out in the city sometime, we go out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We go in threes, three people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One to keep a-- a lit pipe and two people stay on the side way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because this way we were saved.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If somebody attack us, they can give him with the lit pipe over the head.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then they know the-- the Jews doesn't-- doesn't go for this, they'll be killed over nothing or abused for nothing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's how, then, we-- we do this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we try to help our-- ourselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No this is not-- wasn't a solution for a long then anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Our organization, I belong to organization.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They call it Betar, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and we try because we see the future of the Jews in Poland wasn't good anyway.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There's no way out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And no-- no way out anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because the restriction of immigration was all over-- all over Europe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We cannot go no place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we tried to do by unlegal legal immigration to Israel, some way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we organize some way. i remember we organize a-- a walk to Israel, with our organization, a walk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This year was in 1937, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was organized, a couple hundred, maybe thousands of our organization, people rather walking to the border of Romania to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a type of working for propaganda mostly, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The world-- the world looked-- the whole world, they see what we, in some conditions, we would have no way out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we tried this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, this is not the way out anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe a thousand or more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't there because I was in other things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't walk over there, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
